      "raw_id": "RAW-bda2bb8ccc2891ec",
      "start": 356,
      "end": 813
    },
    "source_quote": "Founded in 2022, Stainless has powered the generation of every official Anthropic SDK since the earliest days of our API. Hundreds of companies rely on Stainless to generate SDKs, CLIs, and MCP servers—the libraries, command-line tools, and connectors that let developers and agents use an API. Stainless turns an API spec into SDKs across TypeScript, Python, Go, Java, Kotlin, and more. Each one is fast, reliable, and built to feel native in its language.",
    "extraction_method": "deterministic_source_span",
